{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm-basic/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-grading-students\">1. Grading Students</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#answer\">answer</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-longest-common-prefix\">2. Longest Common Prefix</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#answer-1\">answer</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<h1 id=\"1-grading-students\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-grading-students\" aria-label=\"1 grading students permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. <a href=\"https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/grading/problem\">Grading Students</a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The first line contains a single integer, <code class=\"language-jstext\">n</code>(<code class=\"language-jstext\">1 ≤ n ≤ 60</code>), the number of students.<br>\nEach line of the subsequent lines contains a single integer, <code class=\"language-jstext\">grades[i]</code>(<code class=\"language-jstext\">0 ≤ grades[i] ≤ 100</code>).<br>\nIf the difference between the <code class=\"language-jstext\">grade</code> and the next multiple of <code class=\"language-jstext\">5</code> is less than <code class=\"language-jstext\">3</code>, round <code class=\"language-jstext\">grade</code> up to the next multiple of <code class=\"language-jstext\">5</code>.<br>\nIf the value of <code class=\"language-jstext\">grade</code> is less than <code class=\"language-jstext\">38</code>, no rounding occurs as the result will still be a failing grade.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Original</th>\n<th>Final</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>73</td>\n<td>75</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>67</td>\n<td>67</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>38</td>\n<td>40</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>33</td>\n<td>33</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"answer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#answer\" aria-label=\"answer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>answer</h2>\n<p>The one-liner code</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-jsjava\"><code class=\"language-jsjava\">grade <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">38</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> grade <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> grade <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> grade <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>grade <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"2-longest-common-prefix\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-longest-common-prefix\" aria-label=\"2 longest common prefix permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/longest-common-prefix/\">Longest Common Prefix</a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Find the longest common prefix string amongst an array of strings.</p>\n<p>Example 1: <code class=\"language-jstext\">strs = [\"flower\",\"flow\",\"flight\"]</code>\nOutput: <code class=\"language-jstext\">\"fl\"</code></p>\n<p>Example 2: <code class=\"language-jstext\">strs = [\"dog\",\"racecar\",\"car\"]</code>\nOutput: <code class=\"language-jstext\">\"\"</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"answer-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#answer-1\" aria-label=\"answer 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>answer</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-jsjs\"><code class=\"language-jsjs\"><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">strs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> prefix <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> strs<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>j <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> strs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> strs<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> strs<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> strs<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> prefix\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>j <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> strs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            prefix <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> strs<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> prefix\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Basic Algorithm","date":"November 15, 2021","spoiler":"Mathmatical problems"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm-basic/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}